======================================================================
Scripts to Run Software From Startup
======================================================================

- copy the service file, start_actioncamstreamer.service, to /lib/systemd/system/
- copy the bash script, start_actioncamstreamer.sh, to /actioncamstreamer/
- $ systemctl daemon-reload
- $ systemctl enable start_actioncamstreamer.service
- copy the project binary files to /actioncamstreamer/
